From d489cdf460466ab695eaeb58e00c14722f0c686b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramesh Mandal <ramesh@6epixels.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 14:18:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(messaging): local-first working model - chat, share tab,
 presence

- chat.store.ts: persisted local data layer (contacts, conversations,
  messages) over browser.storage.local, seeded with demo contacts;
  designed so actions swap to API/socket calls when backend lands
- InboxView: conversation list (previews, relative timestamps, unread
  badges) <-> chat thread navigation
- ChatView: message bubbles, shared-link cards (open in new tab via
  browser.tabs.create), simulated typing indicator + canned replies,
  auto-scroll, Enter-to-send composer
- Share current tab: composer action using browser.tabs.query - the
  signature Tabcom move, fully working
- ContactsView: seeded contacts with presence dots, tap to start/open
  a conversation (jumps to Inbox)
- TabBar: live unread count badge on Inbox
- Sign out clears chat data; workspace mount reseeds demo data
- types/chat.ts domain models + time formatting utils
